\
## How It Works\
\
1. System starts and displays "Enter Time (min)" on LCD.\
2. User inputs time using keypad (e.g., 15 for 15 minutes).\
3. Press # to confirm input.\
4. Motor starts running and:\
\
   * LCD shows countdown\
   * Running LED turns ON\
   * Servos move to active position\
   * **Peltier modules operate along with the motor for thermal control**\
5. When time ends:\
\
   * Motor stops\
   * Peltier modules stop\
   * Finished LED turns ON\
   * Servos return to initial position\
6. Press * anytime before starting to clear input.\
\
