\
## Notes\
\
* Ensure proper power supply for motor and Peltier modules\
* Peltier modules require adequate heat dissipation (heat sinks/fans)\
* Do not power motor or Peltier modules directly from Arduino\
* Use common ground for all components\
* Check I2C address of LCD (commonly 0x27)\
\
